        <mxCell id="W2vF0aZWDMr8ijiC13AB-1" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFF88,#FFFF63);strokeColor=#36393d;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);" value="&lt;div&gt;Review represents the rating given by those that have stayed at the Place.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Key attributes:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;+ review: string&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Method:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;+ validate_review()&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;+ submit_review()&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Relatioship:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Bi-association with Place, cant have no ability to review a place.&lt;br&gt;0 to many instances Place has of Review.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Review has 1 instance of Place.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Dependent on User, cant commit reviews without user.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Review has 1 instance of User vice-versa.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
